{"tid":559030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我份工份約係咪有問題","createTime":"2018-02-12T22:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T17:16:01.000Z","uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"847c03c51b6aa5fa8f17ce94e78bf8ce943d49e4","tid":559030,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:15:06.000Z","msg":"勿相認，做緊教畜<br />\n我見工時係寫120一個鐘<br />\n之後話得80<br />\n當時等錢洗，照做<br />\n<br />\n份約話係半職<br />\n一個星期大概20hours<br />\n有少少員工福利<br />\n其實都係睇下獸醫咁 都冇咩特別福利<br />\n<br />\n其實我已經唔想做<br />\n講下原因先<br />\n<br />\n1 本來我講咗唔想番太遠<br />\n公司話okay 但開頭要番遠少少<br />\n因為某分校唔夠人手<br />\n之後就會調我去近啲<br />\n點知只係近兩-三個站<br />\n其實分別不大，我來回都係over三個鐘<br />\n<br />\n2 見工時有講工作範圍包括準備教材，開會同教班<br />\n點知我簽完約先知原來準備教材都幾多份量<br />\n假設如果某同事得4班，<br />\n就淨係準備4份教材<br />\n但我就有好多班，每個月準備&gt;15份<br />\n<br />\n但得教班係有人工<br />\n大家都一樣只計上堂嘅時薪<br />\n番公司開會（一個月一次）同準備教材都冇錢<br />\n我每個月會用多7-10 個鍾做呢啲工作<br />\n上司話我做得慢先係咁<br />\n但我試過快極都要6hours <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3 冇得sick leave<br />\n其實係有嘅，但病咗要照番工<br />\n直到公司搵到同事同你頂更先可以走<br />\n所以我覺得其實同無無分別。<br />\n因為其實未係病到就死都唔會請<br />\n<br />\n4 行內算低人工<br />\n計時薪，低出面10-20%左右<br />\n而我簽完約之後仲有friend邀我做類似工作<br />\n時薪係3倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但撞哂時間，勁後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想辭職<br />\n但睇番份約<br />\n答咗一年約，<br />\n份約寫頭一年如果想離職<br />\n就要3個月前通知加賠償一個月人工<br />\n話係賠比公司重新招聘同訓練員工嘅錢<br />\n其實訓練都係搵個fulltime教你要做乜<br />\n又唔係要聽talk讀course都冇咩特別專業技能<br />\n而且佢係寫賠一個月<br />\n=如果你返4日，就賠4日<br />\n返10日，就賠10日<br />\n所以每個同事嘅賠償金唔同。<br />\n<br />\n又冇寫如果炒你會賠錢比你。<br />\n如果過咗一年後先離職就要4個月通知<br />\n咪變相唔比我搵新工？<br />\n有邊份工接受我話4個月後先番到？<br />\n焗我要失業一排？"},{"pid":"e33f888fb168315276e6f8e6420529dcf06a092f","tid":559030,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb057c059649aa9da21bd3e7995c6fececce8bba","tid":559030,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33f888fb168315276e6f8e6420529dcf06a092f","tid":559030,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37af9f0bb25c6d10c3d65ebfe4f0f0962f3edaf","tid":559030,"uid":84525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:44:15.000Z","msg":"去勞工處問啦 打電話/上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40bd670a13b85db76d02c7b2f6f12616e436d1f","tid":559030,"uid":84525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37af9f0bb25c6d10c3d65ebfe4f0f0962f3edaf","tid":559030,"uid":84525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:44:15.000Z","msg":"去勞工處問啦 打電話/上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:45:10.000Z","msg":"上去佢d度問先岩 上網好似冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d359aeb8062f9a8a327a38104ee2577547d0f20","tid":559030,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e40bd670a13b85db76d02c7b2f6f12616e436d1f","tid":559030,"uid":84525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37af9f0bb25c6d10c3d65ebfe4f0f0962f3edaf","tid":559030,"uid":84525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:44:15.000Z","msg":"去勞工處問啦 打電話/上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:45:10.000Z","msg":"上去佢d度問先岩 上網好似冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:56:44.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔知點咁"},{"pid":"2851b5e45d95